<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P0133: O2 Sensor Circuit Slow Response (sensor 1)
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Cycle duration from rich to lean and lean to rich of HO2S-1 is longer than specified time.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(3 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
HO2S-1 and/or its circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
HO2S-1 heater
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Air intake system
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Exhaust system
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Fuel system
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
